Helm is a tool that automates the creatioyn, packaging, configuration and deployment of kubernetes applications by combining our configuration files into a single reusable package


---------------HELM Installation------------------
https://github.com/helm/helm/releases

wget https://get.helm.sh/helm-v3.14.0-linux-amd64.tar.gz

tar -zxvf helm-v3.14.0-linux-amd64.tar.gz

mv linux-amd64/helm /usr/local/bin/helm

chmod 777 /usr/local/bin/helm  # give permissions 

helm version 




<1>. helm create <project name>
<2>. helm install <release name> <chart name>   #to run helm
<3>. helm upgrade <release name> <chart name>   #for any modifications in previous run
<4>. helm delete <chart name>
<5>. helm list -a
